<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV50">
<l>oṇṇutaṉ māmai yoḷipaya vāmai viraintunantēr</l>
<l>naṇṇutal vēṇṭum valava kaṭākiṉṟu tēṉaviṉṟa</l>
<l>vaṇmuta ṉāyaka ṉīṇmuṭi veṇmutta vācikaittāy</l>
<l>maṇmutal cērvuṟ ṟaruvicey yāniṟku māmalaikkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So as not to cause the sallowing of [her] bright forehead’s darkness, speedily</l>
<l>must our chariot arrive, driver, urgently, – at the great mountain that keeps</l>
<l>making waterfalls, joining the base of the earth, spreading a wreath of white pearls</l>
<l>on the long crown of the liberal primeval leader where honey[-bees] hum.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
